kic and the medieval heroic poems must always be appreciated as poetry in performance, as sound listened to, as words spoken or sung.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aEpic poetry, TurkicxHistory and criticism. 0aEpic poetry. 0aPoeticsxHistoryyTo 1500. 0aPoetry, MedievalxHistory and criticism. 4aEurope. 4aHistory.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Backlist 2000-2013z978311053615740uhttps://doi.org/10.7591/978150173216440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501732164423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501732164/original  a978-3-11-053615-7  Cornell University Press Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles